          {
            "type": "code",
            "content": "```python\nqueue = [S]\nvisited = {S}\n\nwhile queue:\n    node = queue.pop_front()\n\n    for next in node.neighbors:\n        if next not in visited:\n            visited.add(next)\n            queue.push_back(next)\n```",
